lead_paragraph: The Football Association (FA) should follow the lead of their country's rugby counterparts by equipping young players with leadership skills, according to former England rugby coach Stuart Lancaster.

headline.print_headline: England Needs to Develop Leaders, Says Rugby Coach Lancaster
headline.main: England Needs to Develop Leaders, Says Rugby Coach Lancaster
